Process called "get_temp_directory_internal" returns String:
    Note: Get temporary directory with essential runtime calls
    Try:
        Let temp_env be system_call_environment_get with name as "TMPDIR"
        If temp_env is not None:
            Return temp_env
        Otherwise:
            Let temp_env2 be system_call_environment_get with name as "TEMP"
            If temp_env2 is not None:
                Return temp_env2
            Otherwise:
        Note: Fallback: use platform-specific defaults
        Let os_type be detect_operating_system
        Match os_type:
            When Windows:
                Return "C:\\Temp"
            Otherwise:
                        Return "/tmp"
    Catch error:
                Return "/tmp"

